Jorda, E
Mascaró-Galy, G
metadata.dc:description: A case of None Milroy syndrome with chiloabdomen in a 7 year old girl is reported. The most important features are the immunological alterations (depressed delayed immunity in the affected extremity and decreased level of IgA). A review of the literature is made.
metadata.dc:title: Un caso de síndrome de None Milroy asociado a quiloabdomen. Estudio inmunológico
[A case of Nonne-Milroy syndrome associated with chyloabdomen. Immunologic study].
